      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Copy of the payment, through Aphrodisios' bank in the Ö district, in the thirteenth year of Imperator Caesar Domitianus Augustus Germanicus, on the 30th of Mecheir. Harpochras son of Marepsemis, to Marres son of Apynchis: he has received from Harpochras the equivalent of what he owed him according to a (contract) with six witnesses Ö (Here the papyrus breaks off)</ab>
         </div>
